# My Prompt Template Library

## 1. Research Summarizer
Summarize any article in 150 words. Include main argument, 3 key findings, methodology.

## 2. Email Generator
Write professional email. Tone formal/friendly/urgent. 100 words. Include subject line.

## 3. Customer Support Reply
Reply to customer query. Be empathetic. Give solution. Max 3 sentences.

## 4. LinkedIn Post
Write LinkedIn post. Hook + 3 bullet points + question + 3 hashtags.

## 5. Data Extractor
Extract name, order_id, issue_type from text. Output JSON format.

## 6. SEO Meta Description
Write 150-160 character meta description. Include keyword naturally.

## 7. Interview Questions
Generate 5 interview questions for any role. 2 technical + 2 behavioral + 1 problem solving.

## 8. Code Debugger
Debug code. Tell error, why it happened, fixed code.

## 9. Meeting Notes
Summarize meeting notes. Decisions, action items, blockers, next meeting.

## 10. Resume Tailor
Tailor resume for a job. Add keywords, rewrite summary, highlight matching skills.
